description: Facing strong criticism, the royals cut short a trip to Greece they began during a partial lockdown.
title: Coronavirus: Dutch PM concedes 'wrong assessment' over royal holiday
title_page: Coronavirus: Dutch PM concedes 'wrong assessment' over royal holiday - BBC News
maintext: In a statement, the royals said: "We do not want to leave any doubts about it: in order to get the Covid-19 virus under control, it is necessary that the guidelines are followed. The debate over our holiday does not contribute to that."
